  { question: 'How does Selection framework apply to Shopify email marketing app selection (6)?', answer: 'Treat Selection framework as operating discipline, not a one-time checklist. Sequenzy fits lean teams needing lifecycle strategy without profile-tier anxiety; Klaviyo when predictive Shopify data drives weekly send decisions. Revisit quarterly or after catalog, consent, or volume changes.' },
  { question: 'How does Selection framework apply to Shopify email marketing app selection (7)?', answer: 'Treat Selection framework as operating discipline, not a one-time checklist. Sequenzy fits lean teams needing lifecycle strategy without profile-tier anxiety; Klaviyo when predictive Shopify data drives weekly send decisions. Revisit quarterly or after catalog, consent, or volume changes.' },
