    <div class="prose-shopify">
      <h2>Related operator guides</h2>
      <p>Before buying or switching platforms, read <a class="link" href="/guides/selection-framework">selection framework</a> and <a class="link" href="/guides/pricing-models">pricing models</a>. During rollout, pair this guide with <a class="link" href="/guides/implementation-plan">implementation plan</a> and <a class="link" href="/guides/migration">migration</a>. Ongoing ops: <a class="link" href="/guides/segmentation">segmentation</a>, <a class="link" href="/guides/deliverability">deliverability</a>, <a class="link" href="/guides/revenue-attribution">revenue attribution</a>.</p>
